    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In this article, we use testing data as an input of a new epidemic model. We get nice a concordance between the best fit the model to the reported cases data for New-York state. We also get a good concordance of the testing dynamic and the epidemic\u2019s dynamic in the cumulative cases. Finally, we can investigate the effect of multiplying the number of tests by 2, 5, 10, and 100 to investigate the consequences on the reduction of the number of reported cases.</jats:p>",
